Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn‚Äôt just help you craft, it‚Äôs essential to one‚Äôs survival! Four misfits‚ÄîGarrett ‚ÄúThe Garbage Man‚Äù Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)‚Äîfind themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they‚Äôll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative‚Ä¶the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (‚ÄúNinety-Five Senses,‚Äù ‚ÄúNacho Libre‚Äù) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans √ìlafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director‚Äôs creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (‚Äú127 Hours,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), editor James Thomas (‚ÄúPok√©mon: Detective Pikachu‚Äù, the ‚ÄúBorat‚Äù films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), and costume designer Amanda Neale (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúWhat We Do in the Shadows‚Äù). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok,‚Äù the ‚ÄúLEGO¬Æ‚Äù movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie.‚Äù The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

description_vid:
An ADT (Articulated Dump Truck) mining truck is a specialized heavy-duty vehicle used in mining, construction, and quarrying operations to transport large quantities of material like ore, rock, or soil. It's called "articulated" because it has a pivot point between the cab and the dump body, allowing it to better maneuver in rough terrain.

Key features of ADT mining trucks include:

1. High ground clearance and large wheels for navigating difficult terrain
2. All-wheel drive capability for operating in muddy or steep conditions
3. A hinged connection between the cab and dump body that allows for better turning radius
4. Load capacities typically ranging from 25 to 60 tons
5. The ability to operate in conditions where rigid dump trucks cannot

These trucks are particularly useful in mining operations because they can:
- Handle steep grades and poor ground conditions
- Access tighter spaces than traditional rigid dump trucks
- Maintain stability while dumping on uneven ground
- Operate effectively in wet or muddy conditions

Major manufacturers of ADT mining trucks include Volvo, Caterpillar, John Deere, and Bell Equipment. They're generally smaller than rigid-frame mining trucks but offer superior maneuverability and off-road capability.

description_ch:
Step into the untamed world of Saland ‚Äì Where time stands still, and tradition breathes life into every moment.
In Saland, we don‚Äôt just show you nomadic life; we invite you to live it. Join us as we follow a nomadic family that has mastered the art of survival in the wild. Led by a wise grandmother and her tightly-knit tribe of sons, daughters-in-law, and playful grandchildren, this family takes us deep into the heart of Bakhtiari nomadic culture.
Feel the warmth of the open fire as bread bakes in the crisp mountain air.
If you‚Äôve ever wondered what it‚Äôs like to wander freely, to live by the seasons, and to thrive off the land, Saland is your invitation to explore, dream, and embrace the wild beauty of a nomadic legacy.
Are you ready to discover the secrets of a life lived in harmony with the earth? The adventure begins here, in Saland.

This video is for educational and awareness purposes only. The intent is to inform the public about real-life pickpocketing tactics and how to protect themselves. We do not encourage or condone criminal activities.

Extra Tip ‚Äì Beware of Small Front Bags!

Many people think wearing a small bag in front protects them from theft, but experienced pickpockets can still steal from front bags even more easily than backpacks. Why?
 ‚Ä¢ Zippers are more accessible in crowded areas.
 ‚Ä¢ Thieves use distractions to unzip bags unnoticed.
 ‚Ä¢ Thin straps are easy to cut in a second.

üö® 15% OFF ‚Äì Limited-Time Only! üö® Don‚Äôt wait! Use promo code ELYT at https://bit.ly/ElTvYt and score an Annual Pass on EuroLeague TV at 15% OFF! üèÄüéâ

Zalgiris Kaunas rekindled its hopes of reaching the Turkish Airlines EuroLeague postseason after earning a thoroughly deserved 80-86 road win at Crvena Zvezda Meridianbet Belgrade, improving to 13-14 while the home team dropped to 16-11.

Sylvain Francisco served up a masterclass as he sank a game-high 25 points, shooting 6-of-9 from downtown, while Alen Smailagic chipped in with 15 and Deividas Sirvydis added 12 for the Lithuanian outfit.

At the other end, Filip Petrusev paced Zvezda with 16 points but 10 of them came in the first quarter, after which Zalgiris did a grand job containing the Serbian side‚Äôs clutch player. Nemanja Nedovic netted 14 points for the hosts, Joel Bolomboy scored 12 and Codi Miller-McIntyre added 11.

description_ch:
Hailing from different parts of Lithuania and clustered in capital Vilnius, Solo Ansamblis combines internal and external dance moods, electronic and live instruments, analog synthesizers and digitally processed sound. The ever-growing audience entitled their style as sad dance. Solo Ansamblis stands out in the contemporary Baltic music scene with overlapping pulsating synthwaves and mesmerizing live performances. Solo Ansamblis experience unleashes body and sensibility, so you can dance as if nobody's watching. 
The third album Scenos is going to be released by Artoffact Records in 2025. 9 scenes of intersecting time zones and layered realities, tension between the organic and the synthetic, fading memories loss and the flow of time invite listeners to puzzle the various fragments into their own understanding of the universal whole.

title_vid: How to properly attach a sledgehammer, hammer or axe to the handle so that they never fall off #tips
description_vid:
How to properly attach a sledgehammer, hammer or axe to the handle so that they 
never fall off. Useful diy tools ideas. Woodworking ideas and projects.

Few people know this advice and trick of experienced craftsmen. In this video, I will show a simple and incredibly reliable way to put any impact tool, such as a sledgehammer, axe or hammer, on the handle. To do this, you will need a piece of rubber from an old bicycle or motorcycle tube, as well as a few drops of liquid soap. Using this technique for making the tool, it does not break for a very long time, does not fly off and even when struck, the recoil in the hands is reduced.

description_ch:
Justin Flom is a creator, builder, comedian, father and sometimes a magician.

Maverick creator Justin Flom, known as a magician before entering into the realm of social media, has garnered billions of views (about 1.5 billion a month), defying trends, algorithms, and even the #1 rule of magicians. Formerly seen on tours or television tricking celebrities with his magic, Flom is dominating platforms like YouTube and TikTok, crafting content that captivates audiences worldwide. Renowned for his spray paint artistry and the whimsical ‚ÄúTrap-Door-House‚Äù featured in his videos, Flom‚Äôs creative genius transforms ordinary spaces into realms of fantasy and amusement. Unconventional in his approach and a true data analyst, his success lies in his ability to create what the internet likes.

title_vid: The HARDEST Object In Your House...
description_ch:
Former NASA engineer. Current CrunchLabs founder and friend of science.

Answers to some common questions:

1) I make a monthly toy we build together on a video, that gets delivered to your house that teaches you to think like an engineer.  Check it out at- https://crunchlabs.com
2) I studied Mechanical Engineering in School.  I did my undergrad at BYU and Masters at USC.
3) I worked for NASA JPL for 9 years, 7 of which were working on the Curiosity Rover (I made a video about it you should def totes watch cause it's probably my favorite of all my videos).  Then I made some Halloween costumes.  Then I worked for Apple in their Special Projects Group doing Product Design as a Mechanical Engineer for 5 years. Then in 2022 I created CrunchLabs to deliver monthly toys that teach you to think like an engineer.

title_vid: A Speeding Porsche Panamera on Icy Roads Almost Lost Control
description_vid:
A Little Wisdom Helps You Become Smarter !

When driving a Porsche Panamera on a high-speed road with ice and snow, if the speed is a bit too fast and the vehicle starts to get out of control, it can be extremely dangerous. When driving a Panamera on ice and snow, the following aspects should be noted :
 
Vehicle Preparation
 
- Replace Tires : 
Replace the tires with snow tires or winter tires. Their special rubber compound and tread design can provide better grip and handling on ice and snow. If this is not possible, ensure that the tire tread depth is sufficient to effectively drain water and snow, preventing skidding.

- Check Vehicle Systems : 
Conduct a comprehensive inspection of the vehicle before setting out, with a focus on checking whether the braking system, tire pressure, tire pressure monitoring system, electronic stability control system, etc. are in normal operation. Ensure that all vehicle systems can function properly in ice and snow conditions.
 
Driving Skills
 
- Control Speed : 
Adjust the speed according to the road conditions. Generally, the speed should be controlled at 40 - 60 kilometers per hour on ice and snow. Avoid sudden acceleration and sudden braking to prevent the vehicle from skidding and losing control.

- Maintain a Safe Distance : 
Keep a longer distance from the vehicle in front than in normal conditions, at least 2 - 3 times the distance in dry road conditions. This reserves enough reaction and braking distance.

- Steer Smoothly : 
When steering, make gentle movements. Anticipate curves in advance and turn the steering wheel slowly. Avoid making sharp turns, which may cause the vehicle to skid or spin.

- Brake Reasonably : 
Try to use the point braking method and avoid slamming on the brakes. For vehicles equipped with an Anti-lock Braking System (ABS), when braking, keep the brake pedal pressed firmly to let the system function properly.

- Avoid Overtaking : 
Overtaking is very dangerous on ice and snow. If overtaking is necessary, observe the traffic conditions of the vehicles in front and behind carefully. Overtake on a wide and clear section of the road. Turn on the turn signal in advance and complete the overtaking quickly and smoothly after confirming safety.
 
Other Precautions
 
- Pay Attention to Vision : 
Before starting, clean the snow and ice on the vehicle's windshield, rearview mirrors, headlights, and other parts. During driving, use the defrosting and demisting functions reasonably to maintain a good view.

- Monitor Road Conditions : 
Learn about the road conditions and weather information in advance and plan the route. Try to avoid sections with severe icing or prone to accidents. During driving, pay attention to the changes in the road surface and the driving conditions of other vehicles, and adjust the driving strategy in a timely manner.

title_vid: They Left Their Dog Alone on the Top Floor Balcony for Days üíî
description_vid:
#shorts #dog #rescuedog #rescue #husky 

üé• Credit : Yordan Jerez A on TT 

üìñ Full Story :
This man discovered that his neighbors had left their dog on the top floor balcony for three days, without food or water. At first, when he heard the dog crying for help, he thought its owners would come back by evening to take care of it. However, he was completely wrong. Three days later, the dog was still trapped there, all alone and growing weaker from starvation and dehydration. After realizing how bad the situation was, the man quickly called the police, and asked nearby neighbors for help. But at that time, all they could do was give the dog some food and water, just enough to keep it alive.
To everyone‚Äôs surprise, when the police contacted the owners, they said they were still on vacation and couldn‚Äôt return in time, but they promised to send someone immediately to help the dog. Then the next day, the owners did send someone to look after their dog, even though they could have done so much sooner. A few days later, after an investigation, the local animal protection team came to rescue the dog, and took it to a new safer shelter.

Former NASA engineer. Current CrunchLabs founder and friend of science.

2) I studied Mechanical Engineering in School.  I did my undergrad at BYU and Masters at USC.
3) I worked for NASA JPL for 9 years, 7 of which were working on the Curiosity Rover (I made a video about it you should def totes watch cause it's probably my favorite of all my videos).  Then I made some Halloween costumes.  Then I worked for Apple in their Special Projects Group doing Product Design as a Mechanical Engineer for 5 years. Then in 2022 I created CrunchLabs to deliver monthly toys that teach you to think like an engineer.

A new era is born. Watch the Jurassic World Rebirth trailer now. 

-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@jurassicworld
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jurassicworld
X: https://twitter.com/jurassicworld
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jurassicworld
Official Site: https://www.jurassicworld.com/

A new era is born. This summer, three years after the Jurassic World trilogy concluded with each film surpassing $1 billion at the global box office, the enduring Jurassic series evolves in an ingenious new direction with Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Anchored by iconic action superstar Scarlett Johansson, Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey and two-time Oscar¬Æ winner Mahershala Ali, this action-packed new chapter sees an extraction team race to the most dangerous place on Earth, an island research facility for the original Jurassic Park, inhabited by the worst of the worst that were left behind. 

Also starring acclaimed international stars Rupert Friend and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, the film is directed by dynamic visualist Gareth Edwards (Rogue One: A Star Wars Story) from a script by original Jurassic Park screenwriter David Koepp. 

Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, the planet‚Äôs ecology has proven largely inhospitable to dinosaurs. Those remaining exist in isolated equatorial environments with climates resembling the one in which they once thrived. The three most colossal creatures across land, sea and air within that tropical biosphere hold, in their DNA, the key to a drug that will bring miraculous life-saving benefits to humankind.

Academy Award¬Æ nominee Johansson plays skilled covert operations expert Zora Bennett, contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure the genetic material. When Zora‚Äôs operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized by marauding aquatic dinos, they all find themselves stranded on a forbidden island that had once housed an undisclosed research facility for Jurassic Park. There, in a terrain populated by dinosaurs of vastly different species, they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that has been hidden from the world for decades. 

Ali is Duncan Kincaid, Zora‚Äôs most trusted team member; Critics Choice and Olivier Award winner Jonathan Bailey (Wicked, Bridgerton) plays paleontologist Dr. Henry Loomis; Emmy nominee Rupert Friend (Homeland, Obi-Wan Kenobi) appears as Big Pharma representative Martin Krebs and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo (The Lincoln Lawyer, Murder on the Orient Express) plays Reuben Delgado, the father of the shipwrecked civilian family. 

The cast includes Luna Blaise (Manifest), David Iacono (The Summer I Turned Pretty) and Audrina Miranda (Lopez vs. Lopez) as Reuben‚Äôs family. The film also features, as members of Zora and Krebs‚Äô crews, Philippine Velge (Station Eleven), Bechir Sylvain (BMF) and Ed Skrein (Deadpool). 
 
Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by BAFTA winner Edwards from a script by Koepp (War of the Worlds), based on characters created by Michael Crichton. The film is produced by Oscar¬Æ nominee Frank Marshall and Patrick Crowley, both longtime Jurassic franchise producers and of last summer‚Äôs blockbuster, Twisters. The film is executive produced by Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart and Jim Spencer.

description_vid:
Change your car with Carwow: https://bit.ly/Change-Your-Car-2602

When Mat last got his hands on the all-new BMW M5 he was a bit disappointed regarding how it‚Äôs evolved from the previous edition. 

However, now he‚Äôs had the chance to drive it several times, he‚Äôs wondering if he was wrong when he gave his last verdict! To put it to the test, we‚Äôve brought together its key competitors - the RS7 Performance and Mercedes-AMG GT 63.

So of course, given how powerful these machines are, we need to look at the stats! The BMW M5 is powered by a 4.4-litre twin-turbo V8 and an electric motor, which combine to produce 727hp and 1000Nm of torque. Power is sent to all four wheels via an 8-speed auto, weighing a colossal 2,435kg! 

The RS7 is powered by a 4-litre twin-turbo V8, and this creates 630hp and 850Nm. This performance is sent to all four wheels via an 8-speed auto, and it weighs in at 2,065kg. 

Then finally we have the AMG. It‚Äôs also powered by a 4-litre twin-turbo V8, which creates 639hp and 900Nm. It‚Äôs equipped with a 9-speed auto gearbox, and it tips the scales at 2,135kg. 

So the BMW clearly has the performance, but of course, it‚Äôs not like an owner of this car will be drag racing it daily! With that in mind, not only is Mat going to test their performance, but he‚Äôll also give each car a proper Carwow review. He‚Äôll look into their design, their interiors, and what space is like in the rear, and of course, he‚Äôll take each car for a drive. 

So will the new BMW come out on top? Or will the Audi or AMG prevail? You‚Äôll need to keep watching to see for yourself!
